%h1 Regular items

.alert.alert-secondary
  Add the regular items you usually need, organised by #{link_to('groups', groups_path)}.

- if @grouped_items.empty?
  %p.mt-3= link_to 'New item', new_items_regular_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'

- @grouped_items.each do |group|
  %h3= group.name
  = render 'items', items: group.regular_items
  %p.mt-3= link_to 'New item', new_items_regular_path(group_id: group.id), class: 'btn btn-primary'
